title: doc: do not name api index #Index
body:
What steps will reproduce the problem?
1. Visit http://weekly.golang.org/pkg/strings/#Index

What is the expected output? What do you see instead?
The function named "Index" should be focused, and not the Index containing all
function names.

What version of the product are you using? On what operating system?
weekly.2012-02-07

Please provide any additional information below.
Choose a fragment identifier for all headlines that cannot collide with a function name.
